    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The high-revving powerplant breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering a visceral induction note and linear power delivery. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, ensuring the structural integrity matches its performance potential. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and staggered Style 67 alloys, the chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative. While it displays the honest patina of a driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are robust, making it an ideal candidate for the canyon-carving enthusiast.",
