      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power unit. This chassis is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. Maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS service and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventive measure for this platform. The suspension geometry is sharpened by refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring precise turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity and throttle response remain exceptional. A driver-focused example ready for spirited use.",
